<p>I am using "JQUERY unobtrusive" java script for validation. I am using one label and one text box control inside the div tag. When I click on Submit button I need to mark the background color of entire div(divName) as Red.</p>  <pre><code>   &lt;div class="form-group" id="divName"&gt;     &lt;label for="your-name-id"&gt;Your name:&lt;/label&gt;     &lt;input type="text" name="yourname" id="your-name-id" placeholder="Please enter your name"         &lt;/div&gt; </code></pre>